The minor [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] [[Savor Kibbs]] controlled a number of '''followers''', consisting of both [[Human/Legends|Humans]] and [[Gungan/Legends|Gungans]] around the time of the [[Battle of Naboo/Legends|Battle of Naboo]]. Kibbs, a charismatic person and a master of [[Mind trick/Legends|Affect Mind]] held his group together by influencing their minds with [[The Force/Legends|the Force]]. Their goal was to ultimately take control of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]], but they were stopped by members of the disbanded [[Naboo Underground]] movement, who defeated Kibbs and liberated the minds of his underlings.

